com.cafebabe.core

Class JarInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafebabe.core.JarInfo

  • public class JarInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    JarInfo is the representation of the structure that contains the information about classes and methods needed while translating bytecode into CLP clauses. This is essentially information about structure and ordering, as an example we can find numbers of arguments for a method, method numbers, maximus stack size for a method, etc..
    Author:
    Laffineur Gerome
